==English==
===Noun===
'''[[bank]] [[holiday]]''' (plural: '''[[bank holidays]]''')

#(''mainly British'') In [[Great Britain]] and some other countries, a [[weekday]], often a [[Monday]], on which banks were traditionally closed and granted to [[worker]]s as a [[national holiday]].

